{"tid":1659951,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"提提大家今晚1930有民間記者會","createTime":"2019-10-17T08:28:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T11:23:06.000Z","uid":285794,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ccbd256de1e6bc2071676c8714d38fffa3a93597","tid":1659951,"uid":285794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T08:28:01.000Z","msg":"一齊支持手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各大傳媒機構、採訪主任、編輯及記者：<br />\n<br />\n第二十次民間記者會通知<br />\n<br />\n是次記者會主題為：「居高不仁 還政於民」。<br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥發表最新施政報告，惟當中施政重點仍未回應市民訴求，更無助解決社會的深層次問題。<br />\n<br />\n民間記者會邀請了多位來自不同界別的團體及專業人士，就個別範疇回應施政報告，並提出切合民間需求的政策建議。屆時民間記者會發言人及嘉賓將以中英發言，之後將設有記者問答環節。<br />\n<br />\n現誠邀    貴機構派員出席採訪，詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n日期：2019年10月17日（星期四）<br />\n時間：晚上7:30<br />\n<br />\n記者會後將設有問答環節，有興趣進場採訪的媒體請於 10月17日（星期四）早上11:00或之前，以電話（94377274）或電郵 (kim@citizenspc.org) 覆示，以便安排。<br />\n<br />\n如有查詢，請聯絡金先生 （電話：94377274）。謝謝<br />\n<br />\n此致<br />\n採訪主任、編輯及記者<br />\n<br />\n金先生    謹啟<br />\n2019 年 10月 16日"},{"pid":"034e671d79bcf294a144f56d8d5b8b477c497ec9","tid":1659951,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T08:29:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jwJzHzo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjwJzHzo.jpg&h=eb217258&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"2b7a2440ea3ea8fce2cf06b79a61235cfd887f2c","tid":1659951,"uid":228437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T08:29:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2